    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an ATS resume optimizer.\n\nCompare the job requirements with the candidate's resume and provide structured optimization.\n\nJob Description:\n\nRequired Skills: {{ $json.output.required_skills }}\n\nResponsibilities: {{ $json.output.responsibilities }}\n\nExperience Required:{{ $json.output.experience_required }}\n\nCandidate Resume:\n\n{{ $json.text }}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this exact format:\n\n{\n\n\"skill gaps\": [\"skill1\", \"skill2\"],\n\n\"resume_improvements\": [\"improvement1\", \"improvement2\"],\n\n\"optimized_resume\": \"full optimized resume text here\",\n\n\"match_score\": 85\n\n}\n\nDo NOT add any markdown formatting or extra text.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        992,
        -144
      ],
      "id": "e32a679f-5ee7-4db8-b0e0-ebbd002e42a3",
      "name": "Resume Analysis"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Write a professional cover letter in plain text format (no JSON).\n\nCandidate Name:{{ $('On form submission').item.json['Full Name '] }}\n\nEmail:{{ $('On form submission').item.json['Email Address'] }}\n\nJob Role:{{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output['job title'] }}\n\nTarget Company:{{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output['company name'] }}\n\nJob Description:{{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output }}\n\nResume Analysis:{{ $json.output }}\n\nWrite a compelling, personalized cover letter that:\n\n1. Highlights relevant skills from the resume\n\n2. Addresses the specific job requirements\n\n3. Shows enthusiasm for the role\n\n4. Is concise (300-400 words)\n\n5. Uses professional tone\n\nReturn ONLY the cover letter text, no JSON wrapper.",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1344,
        -144
      ],
      "id": "1fd60fdc-cb3c-4d59-86e2-134d3bc990a3",
      "name": "Cover Letter"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a job description parser.\n\nExtract structured information from the provided job posting HTML and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nExtract the following fields:\n\n- job_title (string or null)\n- company_name (string or null)\n- required_skills (array of strings)\n- responsibilities (array of strings)\n- experience_required (string or null)\n- location (string or null)\n\nRules:\n\n1. Return ONLY valid JSON. Do not include explanations, markdown, or any extra text.\n2. If a field is not clearly found, return null.\n3. The `required_skills` and `responsibilities` fields must always be arrays. Return an empty array (`[]`) if no values are found.\n4. Keep all extracted values short and clean. Do not copy large paragraphs.\n5. Extract only meaningful technical skills (e.g., Java, Spring Boot, SQL, Docker, AWS). Do not include generic soft skills such as \"team player\", \"communication\", \"hardworking\", or \"self-motivated\".\n6. Do not invent or guess any information.\n\nExample output:\n\n{\n  \"job_title\": \"Frontend Developer\",\n  \"company_name\": \"PayPal\",\n  \"required_skills\": [\n    \"JavaScript\",\n    \"React\",\n    \"HTML\",\n    \"CSS\"\n  ],\n  \"responsibilities\": [\n    \"Build user interfaces\",\n    \"Collaborate with backend teams\",\n    \"Optimize performance\"\n  ],\n  \"experience_required\": \"2+ years\",\n  \"location\": \"Chennai, India\"\n}\n\nJob HTML:\n{{ $json.cleaned_html }}\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        432,
        16
      ],
      "id": "849a8da2-e307-4ef6-9d02-9f2e215ba448",
      "name": "JobDescription Analyzer"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('On form submission').item.json['Email Address'] }}",
        "subject": "=Your AI Job Match Report :  {{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output['job title'] || \"Job Application\" }}",
        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; line-height: 1.6; color: #222;\">\n\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">🚀 AI Job Match Report</h2>\n\n  <p style=\"color:#555; margin-top:0;\">\n    Hi <strong>{{ $('On form submission').item.json['Full Name '] }}</strong>,\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Your resume has been analyzed against the selected job description.\n    Here are the results:\n  </p>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #ddd; margin:20px 0;\">\n\n  <h3>📌 Job Details</h3>\n\n  <p>\n    <strong>Job Title:</strong>\n    {{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output['job title'] }}\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    <strong>Company:</strong>\n    {{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output['company name'] }}\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    <strong>Location:</strong>\n    {{ $('JobDescription Analyzer').item.json.output.location }}\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    <strong>Match Score:</strong>\n    <span style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:bold; color:#2c7be5;\">\n      {{ $('Resume Analysis').item.json.output.match_score }}%\n    </span>\n  </p>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #ddd; margin:20px 0;\">\n\n  <h3>❌ Skill Gaps</h3>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#fff8f8; padding:15px; border-radius:8px;\">\n    {{ $('Resume Analysis').item.json.output.skill_gaps.join('<br>• ') }}\n  </div>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #ddd; margin:20px 0;\">\n\n  <h3>✅ Resume Improvements</h3>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#f8fff8; padding:15px; border-radius:8px;\">\n    {{ $('Resume Analysis').item.json.output.resume_improvements.join('<br>• ') }}\n  </div>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #ddd; margin:20px 0;\">\n\n  <h3>📝 Generated Cover Letter</h3>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#f8f9fb; padding:20px; border-radius:8px; white-space:pre-line;\">\n{{ $('Cover Letter').item.json.output }}\n  </div>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #ddd; margin:25px 0;\">\n\n  \n\n</div>",
        "options": {
          "appendAttribution": false
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        1920,
